Test vectors are provided in [[bip-0368-test-vectors.json]] and include:

* '''Key-path, no script tree:''' Internal key P, output key Q, 34-byte annex.
* '''Key-path, with script tree:''' Internal key P, merkle root, output key Q, 66-byte annex.
* '''NUMS rejection:''' NUMS point H as internal key, expected KEYPATH_NUMS_BANNED error.
* '''Wrong internal key:''' Mismatched P that doesn't reconstruct Q, expected KEYPATH_TWEAK_MISMATCH error.
* '''Annex format:''' Valid and invalid annex encoding examples.

